name: Faith Cloth Doll
description: 10 inch cloth doll with hand painted face.  Her clothes & body are 100% cotton & stuffed with polyester fiberfil.  Clothes are removable and hair is made from yarn.

name: Simone, the Tooth Fairy
description: Cloth Doll with hand painted face.  She is wearing a felt dress with cotten wings.  She comes with a pillow with a tooth on front.  There is an opening where a childs' tooth can be deposited for safe keeping.  Dress can also be cotten.  Skin tones are brown & tan.  Hair comes in black, brown & red.  Doll is 10 inches tall.

name: Rag Doll
description: Cloth doll with hand embroidered face.  Body & clothes are 100% cotton.  Stuffing is polyester.  Body skin color is brown or tan.  Color of  fabric can be chosen.  Hair color is black, brown or red.  Dolls are approximately 15 inches tall.
